> ### Name: quantile.fdt
> ### Title: Quantile of frequency distribution table (numerical variable)
> ### Aliases: quantile.fdt quantile.fdt.multiple
> 
> ### ** Examples
> 
> library(fdth)
> 
> x <- rnorm(n=1e3,
+            mean=5,
+            sd=1)
> 
> (ft <- fdt(x))
