> ### Name: summary.fdt
> ### Title: Summary methods for fdt objects
> ### Aliases: summary.fdt summary.fdt.default summary.fdt.multiple
> ###   summary.fdt_cat.default summary.fdt_cat.multiple
> ### Keywords: fdt frequency distribution table summary
> 
> ### ** Examples
> 
> library (fdth)
> 
> #=====================
